# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Bigger Keys)

## Summary
The piano now features larger, easier-to-hit keys with balanced sensitivity.

## Improvements
- **Larger Keys**: Height increased to 150px.
- **Balanced Sensitivity**: Threshold set to 0.10 (Not too hard, not too easy).
- **Aim Assist**: Grid lines help you stay in the right lane.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
